---
import ContentSubPageLayout from "../../layouts/ContentSubPageLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Giants";
---

<ContentSubPageLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} bgImage="bg-masters">
  <p>
    Since 1993, Yamin Yamin has been sending voting sheets to experts and
    tournament directors, asking them to list the names of the strongest
    players, in their opinion, who have participated in live tournaments over
    the past two years. The vote results are published on the
    <a href="http://www.flintbg.com/giants.html">website</a>. This way, we get
    to know the names of the top 64 "living" players in the world - the Giants
    of Backgammon.
  </p>
  <figure>
    <img src="../mochy.jpg" alt="Painting: Steen's 'Backgammon Fight'" />
    <figcaption>#1 Masayuki Mochizuki (Mochy)</figcaption>
  </figure>
  <figure>
    <img src="../lylloff.jpg" alt="Painting: Steen's 'Backgammon Fight'" />
    <figcaption>#2 Sander Lylloff</figcaption>
  </figure>
  <figure>
    <img src="../michy.jpg" alt="Painting: Steen's 'Backgammon Fight'" />
    <figcaption>#3 Michihito Kageyama (Michy)</figcaption>
  </figure>
</ContentSubPageLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    margin-left: 3rem;
    margin-right: 3rem;
